"Extrae entidades de la capa de entrada que no se encuentran dentro de los "
"límites de la capa superpuesta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoroverlay.rst:111
msgid ""
"Input layer features that partially overlap the overlay layer feature(s) are"
" split along the boundary of those feature(s) and only the portions outside "
"the overlay layer features are retained."
